  Don't download eds-3.6 patch. It's not needed in -r4.

*pidgin-2.10.7-r5 (14 Aug 2013)
*pidgin-2.10.7-r4 (14 Aug 2013)

  14 Aug 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> -pidgin-2.10.7-r1.ebuild,
  -pidgin-2.10.7-r2.ebuild, -pidgin-2.10.7-r3.ebuild, +pidgin-2.10.7-r4.ebuild,
  +pidgin-2.10.7-r5.ebuild:
  Revbumps for perl stabilization. Committed -r4 with correct perl dependencies
  straight to stable.

*pidgin-2.10.7-r3 (10 Aug 2013)

  10 Aug 2013; Matt Turner <mattst88@gentoo.org> +pidgin-2.10.7-r3.ebuild:
  Update perl dependency for perl without IUSE=build.

  21 Jun 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> pidgin-2.10.7-r2.ebuild,
  -files/pidgin-eds-3.6.patch.bz2:
  Moved compressed patch from portage tree to my dev space.

  20 Jun 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> pidgin-2.10.7-r2.ebuild:
  Small fix to REQUIRED_USE.

*pidgin-2.10.7-r2 (20 Jun 2013)

  20 Jun 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> +pidgin-2.10.7-r2.ebuild,
  +files/pidgin-eds-3.6.patch.bz2, metadata.xml:
  Added mxit protocol as per bug #420819 and added the patch from bug #434212
  to make pidgin compile against >=evolution-data-server-3.6. Converted the
  package to use new python eclass.

  27 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> -pidgin-2.10.4.ebuild,
  -pidgin-2.10.6.ebuild:
  Remove old

*pidgin-2.10.7-r1 (18 Mar 2013)

  18 Mar 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> -pidgin-2.10.7.ebuild,
  +pidgin-2.10.7-r1.ebuild, +files/pidgin-2.10.7-link_sasl_in_irc_plugin.patch,
  metadata.xml:
  Fixed linking sasl with irc plugin (bug #461530). Comitted revbump straight
  to stable. Added epatch_user. Added myself as maintainer.

  14 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> pidgin-2.10.7.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #457580

